node.text: A year ago today was one of the worst days of my life…. I’m still missing you.. I’m still speechless…I’m still in disbelief…i still feel you…I still love you so much. My First baby, my son! You was called home a month before you could even meet ya new baby sister….. she’s so beautiful. You was so excited to meet her, you never left my side. She kicked for you when u kissed my tummy. Crazy because she tossed and turn all thru night out of all nights. She feels you. We feel you. We love you. JUNIE loves and misses you so much y’all grew together literally! Y’all was Frick and Frack lol y’all drove me wild. You loved her so much and was so protective of her and our whole family. Iman misses and loves you so much you was his only son he took you everywhere 😩😂 he didn’t care that u was a full blown big ass wolf dog.. he traveled with you like you was a Poodle in a purse lmfaooo you was his baby! We are broken, we are incomplete without you. We love you forever baby boy. It took me a year to even be able to type “RIP” to you. I miss you so much baby 💔 Basquiat “Boski” Shumpert

Successful people ask questions. They seek new teachers. They’re always learning. 

Personal note to our talented youngins w/ dreams: Stop being afraid to be the student! Stop being afraid of help, stop being afraid to just LISTEN. You don’t have all the answers…. Take in as much knowledge as possible from the ones who’s come before us with the MOST wisdom and knowledge. 

Spike Tey x Spike Lee 🙌🏾 can’t wait for y’all to see what we got comingggggg 👀
